p.d: From Grammy winners to those just starting out, Soul & Jazz LIVE! features artists from around the world performing original material captured as part of a live recorded studio session. Episode 2 includes Camilla George, Terrace Martin, Resolution 88, Push, Rick Leon James, Lindsey Webster, Maurice Brown, Laila Biali, and Misha Mullov-Abbado. Produced by Spacerocket Media for SoulandJazz.com, this is the second in a six-part series featuring performances captured since late 2016.
